data.description: This cozy North Baltimore ranch seeks TLC and a visionary touch. Spacious bedrooms with ample closet space. Family room ready for your choice of flooring, offers potential as a 3rd bedroom or office with private entrance. Bathroom and kitchen will require some TLC. Expansive 2.5 car 936 sq ft garage, outfitted with a built-in workshop, perfect for storage or projects. Set in a location offering easy commutes to Bowling Green, Toledo, and Findlay. Great opportunity for investors or DIY homeowner.
